時隔六年，路易斯-德瑞弗斯於2007年二度客串聲演《辛普森一家》，亦於隔年三度客串。2009年秋季，路易斯-德瑞弗斯與《宋飛傳》卡司群共同客串了拉里·大衛的影集《人生如戲》，該重聚集獲得了陪體的高度關注，並為HBO帶來了不錯了收視。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://mediadecoder.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/07/30/a-seinfeld-reunion-on-curb-your-enthusiasm/ | work=紐約時報 | first=Edward | last=Wyatt | title=A 'Seinfeld' Reunion on 'Curb Your Enthusiasm' | date=2009-07-30 | accessdate=2016-12-06 | archive-date=2021-02-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224184630/https://mediadecoder.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/07/30/a-seinfeld-reunion-on-curb-your-enthusiasm/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2009年，路易斯-德瑞弗斯獲{{link-en|TV Land Award|TV Land Award}}頒發「笑星傳奇獎」，並由好友[[艾米·波勒|艾米·波勒]]頒獎授予。隔年5月4日，為表彰路易斯-德瑞弗斯作為一個女演員與喜劇演員為廣播電視產業上帶來的貢獻，她成為第2407位名留[[好萊塢星光大道|好萊塢星光大道]]的演藝人員，也是《宋飛傳》首位名留星光大道的卡司。其中有段小插曲，即該星星上，路易斯-德瑞弗斯的姓氏缺少了“o”字母以及缺少“-”符號。<ref name="tv.msn.com">{{cite web |url=http://tv.msn.com/tv/article.aspx?news=497765&GT1=28103 |title='Seinfeld' actress is tickled by Walk of Fame typo — MSN TV News |publisher=Tv.msn.com |date= |accessdate=2010-09-01 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68tLOt32W?url=http://tv.msn.com/tv/article.aspx?news=497765 |archive-date=2012-07-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 在該星星被移除並換上更正過後的星星後，路易斯-德瑞弗斯獲得表彰，<ref name="cnnoops">{{cite news | title = Welcome to the Hollywood Walk of... oops! | publisher = CNN, May 4, 2010, David Daniel | url = http://marquee.blogs.cnn.com/2010/05/04/welcome-to-the-hollywood-walk-of-oops/?hpt=C2 | date = 2010-05-04 | accessdate = 2016-12-06 | archive-date = 2012-07-03 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/68tLQT1eu?url=http://marquee.blogs.cnn.com/2010/05/04/welcome-to-the-hollywood-walk-of-oops/?hpt=C2 | dead-url = no }}</ref> 而與路易斯-德瑞弗斯共事過的[[克拉克·格雷格|克拉克·格雷格]]、拉里·大衛、[[艾瑞克·麥柯馬克|艾瑞克·麥柯馬克]]與傑森·亞歷山大皆到場支持。

2010年5月，在《俏媽新上路》製播五季後，CBS宣布取消該劇。<ref>[http://www.ismyshowcancelled.com/article/2010-05-18/no-more-adventures-for-old-christine/ "The New Adventures of Old Christine has been canceled."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ismyshowcancelled.com/article/2010-05-18/no-more-adventures-for-old-christine/ |date=20210423030604 }} May 18, 2010, Is My Show Canceled.com</ref> 對此，主創凱莉·萊瑟嚴正抨擊CBS，認為CBS此舉是性別歧視，<ref name="Digital Spy">{{cite web |last=Wightman |first=Catriona |date=2010-05-20 |title='Old Christine' creator slams show axe |website=digitalspy.com |publisher=[[數碼間諜|數碼間諜]] |url=http://www.digitalspy.com/tv/ustv/news/a220913/old-christine-creator-slams-show-axe/ |accessdate=2016-01-17 |archive-date=2018-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180714164329/http://www.digitalspy.com/tv/ustv/news/a220913/old-christine-creator-slams-show-axe/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |date=2010-05-20 |title=Creator of cancelled Julia Louis-Dreyfus show, 'Old Christine', slams CBS |website=Celebitchy.com |publisher=Celebitchy |url=http://www.celebitchy.com/102033/creator_of_cancelled_julia_louis-dreyfus_show_old_christine_slams_cbs/ |accessdate=2016-01-17 |archive-date=2019-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630184839/https://www.celebitchy.com/102033/creator_of_cancelled_julia_louis-dreyfus_show_old_christine_slams_cbs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Kimbell |first=Trevor |date=2010-05-30 |title=The New Adventures of Old Christine: Cancelled Because of Sexism? |website=tvseriesfinale.com |publisher=TVSeriesFinale |url=http://tvseriesfinale.com/tv-show/new-adventures-of-old-chistine-canceled-15800/ |accessdate=2016-01-17}}</ref> 更表示劇組自始至終都嚴重缺乏電視網的支持，並認為CBS非常浪費路易斯-德瑞弗斯與同劇女演員[[旺達·塞克絲|旺達·塞克絲]]的才華。<ref name="Digital Spy"/> 隨後，製作公司[[華納兄弟電視公司|華納兄弟電視公司]]開始與[[美國廣播公司|ABC]]洽談有關延續該劇的計畫，但最終未能談成。<ref>[http://www.cinemablend.com/television/ABC-Could-Revive-Ghost-Whisperer-And-Old-Christine-24678.html "ABC Could Revive Ghost Whisperer And Old Christine"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cinemablend.com/television/ABC-Could-Revive-Ghost-Whisperer-And-Old-Christine-24678.html |date=20210423030652 }} May 19, 2010, Cinema Blend</ref>

2010年春季，路易斯-德瑞弗斯多次客串了由[[麗莎·庫卓|麗莎·庫卓]]自編自演的網路劇《{{link-en|網療記 (網路劇)|Web Therapy|網療記}}》第三季，該作品後來由[[Showtime電視網|Showtime]]過渡成有線[[網療記_(電視劇)|同名電視影集]]，而路易斯-德瑞弗斯的戲份於2012年的第二季登場。<ref>[http://www.digitalspy.ie/ustv/news/a392047/lisa-kudrow-on-web-therapy-character-fiona-is-a-terrible-person.html Lisa Kudrow on 'Web Therapy' character: 'Fiona is a terrible person'] 數碼間諜. (July 6, 2012).</ref>

2010年秋季，路易斯-德瑞弗斯於同樣出身自《週六夜現場》的[[蒂娜·菲|蒂娜·菲]]自編自演之NBC艾美獎獲獎喜劇《[[超級製作人|超級製作人]]》中，客串演出蒂娜·菲飾演之女主角{{link-en|麗茲·萊蒙|Liz Lemon}}之想像版。11月1日，她亦於參演了《週六夜現場》特輯的演出。

=== 2011–至今：《副人之仁》 ===
[[File:Vice_President_Joe_Biden_jokes_with_Julia_Louis-Dreyfus.jpg|thumbnail]]於[[白宮|白宮]]合影]]
2011年5月至6月，路易斯-德瑞弗斯與丈夫布拉德·霍爾時隔多年繼《凝視艾莉》後再度合作，共同製作了短片《{{link-en|紀錄巴黎|Picture Paris}}》。該劇由霍爾編導、由路易斯-德瑞弗斯主演，並在2012年1月29日於{{link-en|聖芭芭拉國際電影節|Santa Barbara International Film Festival}}首映，而影評家給予該作品不錯的評價，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pictureparisfilm.com/ |title=PICTURE PARIS - Home Page - Julia Louis-Dreyfus in PICTURE PARIS |publisher=Pictureparisfilm.com |date= |accessdate=2013-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130218194635/http://www.pictureparisfilm.com/ |archive-date=2013-02-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> HBO則於2012年12月17日在小螢幕上首播。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J162eUcKst0 |title=HBO Picture Paris Preview |publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]] |date=2012-11-21 |accessdate=2013-02-20 |archive-date=2021-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210428182752/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J162eUcKst0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2011年初，HBO證實路易斯-德瑞弗斯將在新諷刺喜劇《[[副人之仁|副人之仁]]》中飾演主角瑟琳娜·麥爾副總統，同時也將身兼影集製作人。<ref>[http://www.afro.com/sections/arts_entertainment/story.htm?storyid=72668 "HBO Begins Filming of 'VEEP' in Maryland<"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.afro.com/sections/arts_entertainment/story.htm?storyid=72668 |date=20140203045750 }} October 5, 2011, Afro.com</ref> 為了詮釋角色，路易斯-德瑞弗斯參訪了[[阿爾·戈爾|阿爾·戈爾]]等數位前美國副總統、<ref>[http://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/tv/actress-julia-louis-dreyfus-says-she-talked-with-2-us-vice-presidents-for-new-hbo-comedy/2012/01/13/gIQADqzKxP_story.html "Julia Louis-Dreyfus says she researched role in HBO comedy by chatting up 2 US vice presidents"]華盛頓郵報 {{Wayback|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/tv/actress-julia-louis-dreyfus-says-she-talked-with-2-us-vice-presidents-for-new-hbo-comedy/2012/01/13/gIQADqzKxP_story.html |date=20190513080056 }}</ref> 參議員、演講稿人、各辦公室官員及調度員等政治活動人物。<ref name="Fresh Air">{{cite web |title=Fresh Air with Terry Gross, May 3, 2012: Interview with Julia Louis-Dreyfus; Interview with Steven Moffat; Review of the film "The Avengers." |date=2012-05-03 |url=http://www.worldcat.org/title/fresh-air-with-terry-gross-may-3-2012-interview-with-julia-louis-dreyfus-interview-with-steven-moffat-review-of-the-film-the-avengers/oclc/958462148 |website=Fresh Air with Terry Gross
|publisher=National Public Radio (U.S.) WHYY, Inc. |quote="Scroll down to  'View online' to hear the audio of the interview."}}</ref> 路易斯-德瑞弗斯更公開讚揚HBO給予卡司及劇組“足夠的前期製作”，其中包括在開拍前的六個月排練。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://articles.latimes.com/2012/jun/07/news/la-en-welcome-back-20120607/2 | work=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]] | title=The view from three TV veterans | first=Christy | last=Grosz | date=2012-06-07 | accessdate=2016-12-06 | archive-date=2015-09-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150920032839/http://articles.latimes.com/2012/jun/07/news/la-en-welcome-back-20120607/2 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

